                                 <td style="font-family:Avenir,Helvetica,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;padding:35px">
                                    <span class="im">
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><strong><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'><a href="{{url('community-guidelines')}}">COMMUNITY PAGES - GUIDELINES</a></span></strong></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>My Health Squad&rsquo;s community is meant to be a resource where members can benefit from the experience of other members and select experts. The community is a safe and inclusive space where all members conduct themselves with integrity, honesty and respect.</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>Please direct any questions or feedback to&nbsp;</span><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:yellow;'><a href="mailto:community@myhealthsquad.ca">community@myhealthsquad.ca</a></span><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>&nbsp;(*) and review our privacy policy at (</span><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:yellow;'><a href="{{url('privacy-policy')}}">here</a></span><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>).</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>Be positive, respectful and inclusive.</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Offensive content, explicit content and swearing are not allowed.</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Do not post abusive, threatening, slanderous, profane, content or be disrespectful or belligerent against any member or group of members.</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Keep it positive!</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Posts that go against the spirit of positivity and collaboration will be removed.</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>&nbsp;</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>Share Ideas, experiences and questions.</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The is an 18+ community.</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Designated vendors chosen to field specific questions relevant to their area of knowledge will be present in the community and are expected to give free and unbiased advice when asked.</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Buyin, selling, and advertising, is not allowed in the Community. Soliciting, including votes, participation in surveys, and market research is also not allowed.</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Non-wedding related conversations will be removed.</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Do not share the personal information of another member without their consent.</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Do not claim expertise you don&rsquo;t have or falsely represent yourself.</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>Users Acknowledgements</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; No multiple accounts allowed.</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Don&rsquo;t reveal your contact information or anything else you want to remain private in a community chat.</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Keep you chat in the appropriate groups. My Health Squad may reorganize chats to make them easier to find and categorize as needed.</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;/*font-size:15px;*/font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";color:#222222;background:white;'>&middot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Absolutely no promoted content or redirecting traffic to sites that force the download of a virus, spyware, programs, or other content.</span></p>
